Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon the discovery\Nof Aizen's true goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:37.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the fierce battle between Soul Society\Nand Hueco Mundo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:40.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has been taken to\Na whole new level.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The showdown will be in winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:50.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we must hone our skills...\Nand prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, Sado, and Ishida\Nundergo harsh training
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:58.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in preparation for the impending\Nshowdown with Aizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya's advance troops\Nalso remain in Karakura Town
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:04.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and continue to guard the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, a new Arrancar appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:13.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku protects the soul of\Na boy named Shota
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who happens to be at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:19.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But the incident doesn't end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:26.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That murky Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that\NMock Arrancar this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, I'm going to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where that whistling is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:41.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You go home by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:43.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:52.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if that Arrancar from\Nthis evening has allies nearby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:57.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! But in return,\NI want you to stick close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! All right, Ms. Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:02.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:40.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Help... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't just its Spiritual Pressure\Nthat's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It even looks the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks exactly like the one\NIkkaku killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there two look-alikes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!\Nwe're capturing it alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you've caught me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A third one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And a fourth one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.\NThey're Arrancars that look the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:05.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many\Nof us you defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Ayasegawa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are currently battling\NMock Arrancars...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We detected the Spiritual Pressure of \Nthe Mock Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that we encountered earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the signal\Nand encountered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this the guy that\NIkkaku killed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:42.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:46.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madarame! Ayasegawa!\Nwe're in combat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can multiply!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Exterminate them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot simpler that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Things will never end\Nat this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's lead them into a wide area\Nand crush them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What wide area?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that park\Nwe saw earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, go ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nowhere to\Nescape to anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:24.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Frost unto the Heavens, Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika! Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you both all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys weren't\Na problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:14.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they were troublesome\Nbecause of their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to capture at least\None of them alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:29.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:50.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui! Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:51.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yui! She's my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui! Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:23.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like\Nanything's wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a normal soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Yui?\Nwe're safe here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:33.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing you said that\Nyou had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to find\Nyour sister, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all in a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad, my mom, Yui and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to\Nthe amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}See? Isn't that a nice sound,\Nbig brother?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:15.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a lot of noise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to,\NI had this chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And my dad and my mom\Nwere gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you were searching\Nfor your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui... Can you tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!\NThank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:12.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she suddenly\Nappear in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:17.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota... You're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukitake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Captain Hitsugaya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like you're having quite\Na bit of trouble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:31.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about the Arrancar\Nyou encountered...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to let someone from{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Department of Research and\NDevelopment tell you their findings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Akon of the Department of\NResearch and Development.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're told the Arrancar that\Nyou defeated appeared once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:54.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Furthermore, he multiplied\Nbefore our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:57.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed all of them\Nthat were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure if\Nthat's the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I checked a record of\Nthe Spiritual Pressure in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it matched that of all\Nthe multiplied Mock Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:15.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, when they split,\Nthey aren't separate entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, they form a single colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that they share\Na single consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that this Arrancar moves\Nseveral clones at once
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to absorb as\Nmany souls as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:35.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like worker ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their main body is probably\Nhiding somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and giving orders to the clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any way to find out\Nwhere their nest is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is difficult to pinpoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the report,\Nwhenever they appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there's always a whistling sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:56.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:01.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever it appeared,\Nwe always heard that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound restrains their victims,\Nand controls their movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:18.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shall analyze that sound\Nso that we can pinpoint{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when they will appear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Things sure have become troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've bought some bento boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously though...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always impressed by\Nthese "convenience stores."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with rice balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they even sell these in\Nthe middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! They brought some\Nbento boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put together our plan\Nafter we've had something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, about the Mock Arrancar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already gone over\Neverything we know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:04.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case,\Nwe must spread out over a large area
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and prepare to quickly deal\Nwith various situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that about sums it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this will keep me\Nfrom getting bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take turns watching the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, you stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and watch these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we perform a Konso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No... We can do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're very kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:38.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These siblings have\Nfinally come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:44.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to let them stay\Ntogether for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love a bath before work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how's Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally got to see Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:17.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were behaving strangely\Nwhen my captain asked you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:24.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,about what happened in\Nthe park this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep it to yourself.\NTell me about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:02.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body's moving on its own...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's appeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:14.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:27.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How repulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Captain! Ikkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay!\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:57.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think she's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just now...\NI sensed that Arrancar's--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:53.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here!\NWe've got to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:11.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll look for Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:17.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect Yui myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:45.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui! What were you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to come to this park.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're here,\NI'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I...ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui... I left her here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:31.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.64,0:23:21.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An Arrancar that multiplies...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:24.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you leave one,\Nthey'll keep multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.\NI was just thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We could fight as much as we wanted\Nwith one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:30.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to capture one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:31.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty energetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:34.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably got a stupid idea\Ninto their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:37.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N- Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:39.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we always use this room\Nas if it's ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:42.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:45.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime went to Soul Society\Nwith Kuchiki,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:46.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's completely all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:48.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Well, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:53.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I am sad that I can't eat\NOrihime's delicious cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:56.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? She's really good at cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.59,0:23:59.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to try some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:01.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:02.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?